Drill 2 — Clean Revenue vs Adjustment-Heavy Revenue Run-Rate
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Exact task statement
For each Entity, vertical, BU, and LOB, compare clean operating revenue with adjustment-heavy revenue by month. Then assess whether the latest month is above or below recent clean run-rate.
Build order
5.	Apply the fixed clean-versus-adjustment mapping.
6.	Aggregate to revenue_month, entity, vertical, bu, lob.
7.	Calculate clean_revenue, adjustment_revenue, total_revenue, and clean_share_pct.
8.	Add trailing_3m_clean_avg and compare the latest clean revenue with that average.
Validation checks
•	clean_revenue plus adjustment_revenue must equal total_revenue.
•	Segment totals must roll up to company totals.
•	Trailing averages must use full closed months only.
  
Output column definitions
•	clean_share_pct = clean_revenue / total_revenue.
•	trailing_3m_clean_avg = average clean revenue across the latest 3 closed months within the same segment.
•	run_rate_gap_pct = (clean_revenue - trailing_3m_clean_avg) / trailing_3m_clean_avg.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Solution (Partial) - Have not calculated the percentage values.
--------------------------------------------------------------------

With cte_1 as(
Select	
	revenue_month,
	rev_mth_dt,
	entity,
	Sum(clean_revenue_amount) as sales_invoice,
	(Sum(credit_memo_amount) + Sum(debit_memo_amount)) as memo_amount,
	(Sum(accrual_amount) + sum(adjustment_revenue_amount) + Sum(manual_amount)) as adjustment_amount,
	(Sum(clean_revenue_amount) + Sum(credit_memo_amount) + Sum(debit_memo_amount) + 
	Sum(accrual_amount) + Sum(adjustment_revenue_amount) + sum(manual_amount)) as total_revenue
From platinum.segment_month_base
Group by 
	revenue_month,
	rev_mth_dt,
	entity
Order by
	rev_mth_dt desc
),
cte_2 as
(
Select 
	c.rev_mth_dt,
	c.entity,
	p.is_trailing_3m,
	c.sales_invoice,
	c.memo_amount,
	c.adjustment_amount,
	c.total_revenue,
	Max(c.revenue_month) over() max_mth
From cte_1 c
Left Join platinum.period_reference p
On c.rev_mth_dt = p.month_start
Where p.is_trailing_3m = 1
Order by rev_mth_dt Desc
),
cte_3 as(
Select
	rev_mth_dt,
	entity,
	sales_invoice,
	memo_amount,
	adjustment_amount,
	total_revenue,
	Round((Avg(total_revenue) over(partition by entity))::numeric,2) avg_3m_revenue,
	max_mth
From cte_2
--Where extract(month from rev_mth_dt) = max_mth
Group by
	rev_mth_dt,
	entity,
	sales_invoice,
	memo_amount,
	adjustment_amount,
	total_revenue,
	max_mth
Order by rev_mth_dt desc
)
Select
	rev_mth_dt,
	entity,
	sales_invoice,
	memo_amount,
	adjustment_amount,
	total_revenue,
	avg_3m_revenue
From cte_3
where 
	extract(month from rev_mth_dt)::numeric = max_mth


